The course teaches to express oneself at a lower intermediate level, both orally and in written form. The course is based on texts and grammar and lexical exercises. The seminars will be conducted in a practical way.
The course assumes an active participation from the students in making dialogues, in expressing their views on the themes treated, it also assumes composition of short texts.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to acquire the lower intermediate level of Spanish.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  At the end of this course, students will have acquired a command of Spanish conversation formulas and grammar at lower intermediate level, the knowledge of basic vocabulary and its use in conversation and in written form.
